Title: Single-cell analysis of samples from healthy human colon
Description: ATACseq and RNAseq data obtained by the colon tissues analysis. Samples were collected from adult human donors.

Title: PBMC Data Set
Description: PBMC from a Healthy Donor - Granulocytes Removed Through Cell Sorting (10k)

Title: scATAC-seq and unpaired scRNA-seq of hematopoetic cells
Description: Example scATAC-seq data of hematopoietic cells included in ArchR package was integrated with scRNAseq. ScATAC-seq data was obtained from GSE139369 and scRNA-seq obtained from https://jeffgranja.s3.amazonaws.com/ArchR/TestData/scRNA-Hematopoiesis-Granja-2019.rds

Title: LNCaP Cells Treated with Enzalutamide
Description: Multiome data (scATAC and scRNAseq) for enzalutamide-treated LNCaP cells. Measured (unpaired) with Illumina NextSeq 500 (GPL18573). Results stored in GEO, acc.nos: GSE168667 and GSE168668.

Title: Reprogram-seq of LNCaP cells
Description: scMultiome data of LNCaP infected with FOXA1, NKX2-1, GATA6
